Exception la mot su kien khong mong muon ma khi xay ra no se lam gian doan chuong trinh dang chay
    
Khi Exception xay ra thi chuong trinh ket thuc ngay tai do

Neu Exception khong xay ra thi code o trong catch block se khong duoc chay

Co the catch duoc nhieu hon 1 kieu Exception

Moi Exception co mot cach catch block khac nhau

catch (Exception e) --> De chup het tat ca Exceptions

Cau truc chung thuong la:
+ Try 
+ 1 hoac nhieu Catch block
+ Finally (code luon luon dc chay, thuong thi dev dung block nay de dong cac connection hoac nhung file ma ta dang doc)

Chu y: Khi Exception xay ra o dong code nao trong try block thi tat ca cac dong code sau cai dong code do se ko dc chay nua